## Terraform
- [IAC-01] **MUST** pin providers; use remote state with locking; type variables; sensible defaults.
- [IAC-02] **SHOULD** use reusable modules (registry, cluster, VPC/VNet, DB); avoid copy-paste.

## Security & Secrets
- [IAC-SEC-01] **MUST NOT** output sensitive values; integrate with a secret manager.
- [IAC-SEC-02] **MUST** run plan → review → apply via CI; schedule drift detection.
